text: Incisa in Val d'Arno was a comune in the Metropolitan City of Florence in the Italian region of Tuscany. On 1 January 2014, the former municipalities of Figline Valdarno and Incisa in Val d'Arno merged to form the new municipality of Figline e Incisa Valdarno. Category:Former municipalities of the Metropolitan City of Florence
title: Incisa in Val d'Arno
